Your all-inclusive medicine delivery platform
Contactless medicine delivery straight to your door.

How Medisend Works

1. Order your medicine

Using the Medisend app, choose your pharmacy and place an order.

2. Pharmacy receives order

After your order is sent in, the pharmacy will review and fulfill your order.

3. Your medicine delivered

A trusted delivery driver will pick up your medication and deliver it straight to you.
